latestIgtvVideos.title: Boomi Coffee Ad - Sirisha Thatakula
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
With 3.4 billion people in lockdown across the globe, 2020 has been the most adventurous year for everyone in the world. The year had Panic, disbelief, suffering for some, Yet, it gave peace, calm and healing for some. It had taught us many good life's lessons...Gave great opportunities to some of us. Taught us that there is always something to look forward to.
 
Though I have been Modelling and promoting many Brands and businesses over the past 7+ years, I Have done more creative online activities in 2020, that kept me from boredom. This not only helped the businesses and brands that I've promoted but also kept me on my toes during this turbulent year. The trend continues in 2021...

One such opportunity is working for Boomi Coffee . When they approached me to put together some ad-Video, to promote for the welfare of native tribes in Araku valley, who dedicated their lives on hill stations producing fresh coffee. I couldn't say no. 

And What good is it to work alone? I tagged along my cheerful friends Nirathi Rao Kalavapudi , @Sharmila Mekala, Preeti and Neha Kanagarla, tied up with the budding videographer and an excellent photographer Krishna from Khoto films -  This is the end product!!!

BTW - as you all know, I never promote anyone or anything, unless I believe personally that they are good. Boomi Coffee IS THE BEST! Must try!
